Diana with a rose



For our twelfth anniversary, we went to dinner at the Albion River Inn.
This is the view from the lawn below the restaurant, just outside the window from our table.
Taken Tuesday, July 03, 2001, 06:49:21pm.  Original image size: 1600x1200, 1030kb
